Cush Jumbo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cush_Jumbo 0 Cush Jumbo (born 23 September 1985) is an English actress and writer. She wrote and starred in a one-woman show, Josephine and I. In 2011, she won the Ian Charleson Award for young actors as Rosalind in As You Like It and received an Olivier nomination in 2012 as Mark Antony in an all-female cast of Julius Caesar. She played attorney Lucca Quinn in the seventh season of the US drama series The Good Wife on CBS and its spinoff The Good Fight on CBS All Access.
